Package: speedfetch
Version: 1.1-1
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Fast Linux system information fetcher with 500+ distro logos
 SpeedFetch is a minimalist and fast C++ utility for displaying
 Linux system information with beautiful ASCII art of the distribution.
 Supports 500+ Linux distributions with colored terminal output.
 .
 Features:
  - Display 26+ system information fields
  - 500+ distribution logos with color support
  - Fast hardware and software detection
  - Customizable configuration
  - Linux Mint and all major distros support
  - Font, theme, cursor, and terminal detection
